						<div class="postbody">Are the movie files not simply the recordings of what was read back from each $4016/4017 poll? If not, why? Can still decode that to show button presses onscreen if desired.
<br />
<br />Wouldn't help emulator synchronization much, but makes supporting any input peripheral automatic, and avoids at least some timing issues.</div>

